<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an König Sigismund I.</head><p>Der Rat listet die Fürsten, Herren, Bischöfe und städtischen Vertreter, die zu der vom Adressaten einberufenen Reichsversammlung bereits in Nürnberg eingetroffen sind.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_261" id="129v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_261_r2l1"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Sıgmund<ex>en</ex></expan> Römıſchem künıg ʒu allen ʒeıten merer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r2l2">des Reıchs vnd ʒu <expan>Vng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ʒu Beheim Dalmacıen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r2l3">Croacıen etc künıg / <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_261_r2l4"><expan>Alldurchleẅchtıgıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> furſt vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . <expan>Vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnd<ex>er</ex>tenikeıt</expan> ſchuldıg vnd wıllıg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r2l5">dıenſt ſeyn <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>künigl<ex>ich</ex></expan> maıeſtat mıt <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleıſſ bereyt / <expan>Gnedıgıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r2l6"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / als eẅr <expan>künigl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>durchleẅchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> . <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnedıge<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ den <expan>kurfürſte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r2l7">fürſten vnd <expan>Stett<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu dem <expan>heılıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Römıſche<ex>n</ex></expan> Reıche gehörend <expan>v<ex>er</ex>bodt</expan> hat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r2l8">auf dıſʒ cʒeıt cʒu <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>künıgl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> gen <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> <expan>ʒukome<ex>n</ex></expan> / Alſo bıtten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r2l9">wır eẅr <expan>künıgl<ex>ich</ex></expan> maıeſtat <expan>ʒuwıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> gnedıg <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ dıe <expan>Ercʒbıſch<ex>öfe</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r2l10">von Meıncʒ vnd von Tryer vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> Ludweıg von der Pfallncʒ . / mit = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r2l11">ſampt <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ dem <expan>Bıſch<ex>of</ex></expan> von Speyr vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> <expan>Stepf<ex>an</ex></expan> vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r2l12">Otten <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>brud<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ~ dem <expan>lantgraf<ex>en</ex></expan> von Heſſen vnd etwıeuıl <expan>grafe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r2l13"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> / vnd vnſer <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ~ der <expan>Bıſch<ex>of</ex></expan> von <expan>vvırcʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> auf den <expan>nehſtuergangen<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r2l14">ertag des nu acht tag ſeyn . bey vns ʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> <expan>eıngerıtte<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeyn Vnd ſeıd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r2l15"><expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> ʒeıt ſo ſeyn ʒu vns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ der <expan>Ercʒbıſch<ex>of</ex></expan> von Maylan </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r2l16">~ der <expan>Bıſch<ex>of</ex></expan> von Paſſaw ~ der Patrıarch von fryawl vnd ~ der Legat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r2l17">mıt Jn . Darnach ſeyn ʒu vns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> . vnſer <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> <expan>Johan<ex>n</ex>s</expan> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r2l18">Peyern ~ der Marggraf von Baden vnd ~ der <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> von Schalawn . So </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r2l19">wartt man auf heẅt <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ des <expan>Ercʒbıſch<ex>ofs</ex></expan> von Cöln </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r2l20">bey vns <expan>eincʒureıte<ex>n</ex></expan> . So ſeyn auch von vıl <expan>Stette<ex>n</ex></expan> vom Reyn von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r2l21">Elſeſſ von Swoben vnd von franken <expan>bottſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> bey vns / Das tun wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r2l22">eẅr <expan>künıgl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> als eẅr getreẅ vndertan vmb des beſten <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r2l23">alſo ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>künıgl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> maıeſtat <expan>vnd<ex>er</ex>tenikeıt</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r2l24">dıenſt vnd <expan>gefalle<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>beweıſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>möchte<ex>n</ex></expan> / Das teten wır mıt <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r2l25">wıllen <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / <expan>Scrıptu<ex>m</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_261" id="129v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Sigmund<ex>en</ex></expan>, römischem künig, zu allen zeiten merer
                        des reichs und zu <expan>Ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, zu Beheim, Dalmacien,
                        Croacien etc. künig, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Alldurchlewchtigist<ex>er</ex></expan> furst und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>und<ex>er</ex>tenikeit</expan> schuldig und willig dienst seyn
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>künigl<ex>ich</ex></expan> maiestat mit
                            <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiss bereyt.
                                <expan>Gnedigist<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als ewr <expan>künigl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>durchlewchtik<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnedige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> den <expan>kurfürste<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        fürsten und <expan>stett<ex>en</ex></expan> zu dem
                            <expan>heilig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>römische<ex>n</ex></expan> reiche gehörend
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>bodt</expan> hat, auf disz czeit czu
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>künigl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> gen <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
<expan>zu kome<ex>n</ex></expan>, also bitten wir ewr
                                <expan>künigl<ex>ich</ex></expan> maiestat <expan>zu
                            wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> gnedig
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> die
                            <expan>erczbisch<ex>öfe</ex></expan> von Meincz und von Tryer und
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan> Ludweig von der Pfallncz mitsampt
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> dem <expan>bisch<ex>of</ex></expan> von Speyr
                        und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
<expan>Stepf<ex>an</ex></expan> und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan> Otten,
                                <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>brud<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, dem <expan>lantgraf<ex>en</ex></expan> von
                        Hessen und etwievil <expan>grafe<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> und unser <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>
                        der <expan>bisch<ex>of</ex></expan> von <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan><app>
<note><q type="date">auf den <expan>nehstvergangen<ex>en</ex></expan>
                                    ertag, des nu acht tag seyn,</q>15.04.1421</note>
</app> bey uns zu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
<expan>eingeritte<ex>n</ex></expan> seyn. Und seid
                            <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan> zeit so seyn zu uns
                                <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> der <expan>erczbisch<ex>of</ex></expan> von
                        Maylan, der <expan>bisch<ex>of</ex></expan> von Passaw, der patriarch von
                        Fryawl und der legat mit in; darnach seyn zu uns
                            <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> unser <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
<expan>Johan<ex>n</ex>s</expan> von Peyern, der marggraf von Baden und der
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> von Schalawn; so wartt man auf hewt
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> des <expan>erczbisch<ex>ofs</ex></expan> von
                        Cöln bey uns <expan>einczureite<ex>n</ex></expan>; so seyn auch von vil
                                <expan>stette<ex>n</ex></expan> vom Reyn, von Elsess, von Swoben und
                        von Fanken <expan>bottsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> bey uns. Das tun wir ewr
                                <expan>künigl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> als ewr getrew undertan umb des besten
                                <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> also zu
                            <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>künigl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> maiestat
                            <expan>und<ex>er</ex>tenikeit</expan> dienst und
                                <expan>gefalle<ex>n</ex></expan>
